In data-table.tsx lines 149-155, the onContextMenu handler for headers has identical branches:

```
if (isGrouped) {
  header.column.toggleGrouping();
} else {
  header.column.toggleGrouping();
}
```

Both branches do the same thing. This is either dead code (simplify to just `header.column.toggleGrouping()`) or the else-branch was meant to do something different (e.g., start grouping on a non-grouped column vs removing grouping).
